casebody.data:
The State ex rel. Azizhakim, Appellant, v. Gaul, Judge, Appellee.

[Cite as State ex rel. Azizhakim v. Gaul (1993), 68 Ohio St.3d 115.]

*116(No. 93-1422 Submitted November 9, 1993 Decided December 29, 1993.) Ali Azizhakim, pro se. Stephanie Tubbs Jones, Cuyahoga County Prosecuting Attorney, and Karen L. Johnson, Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellee.

The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
